description.en: ISITDEBUNKED Ltd. is a media company registered in England and Wales under the company registration number: 13168316. We are striving to bring about a more fact-checked world that's decentralised from the original fact-checkers who some may call activists on occasion due to their picking and choosing which facts to publish and say is legitimate and which ones to ignore that it has been debunked to serve usually a political purpose but could also be other reasons that they may decide to give false information but either way we disagree with this and want to establish a network that is ran by community and the community users to be rewarded for their contributions to the system, for example. Debunking a news report will be rewarded by the system with Debunk (DBNK) Token built on Ethereum as an ERC-20 token.
